org.apache.paimon.fs

Class Path

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.fs.Path
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Path>

    @Public
public class Path
extends Object
implements Comparable<Path>, Serializable
    Names a file or directory in a FileIO. Path strings use slash as the directory separator.
    Since:
    0.4.0
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
